dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
Dear Android Marketplace,

We recently became aware of a blatant copyright violation and I seek  
immediate relief from Google.   The Developer/ seller inoX Labs has
created  
a game called 'Finger Slaughter' which is a copy of our game Finger  
Slayer.  Hugely popular game on the iPhone! (Information On Finger Slayer
